Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们整个上午都在翻亚特伍德的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've been digging through Atwood's office all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道怎么回事吗  -内部检查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know what's going on? - It's an internal review.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特伍德为什么会被内部调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is Atwood being investigated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know that's what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为内部调查的老大走过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because here comes the Director of Internal Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·法索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借一步说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A word?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字是加百利·汤普森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His name is Gabriel Thompson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去二十年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He worked as a systems analyst
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直担任国家安全局的系统分析员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the National Security Agency for the last 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}国安局\N机密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他昨天就这样带着大批机密资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yesterday he just walked out the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出国安局大门吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a ton of classified information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早  国安局宣布这是一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which this morning the NSA is calling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-极度严重的信息泄露  -有多严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- a "Significant breach." - How significant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤普森拿走的硬盘原型机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the prototype hard drive Thompson took
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够保存万亿字节的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is capable of storing terabytes of files.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国安局估计需要耗费多日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NSA estimates it'll take days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能梳理系统  评估失窃数据情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to comb through the system and assess the stolen data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的话  别让媒体听到风声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luckily, the press hasn't gotten wind of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们早晚会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, only a matter of time before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意  我们对这个汤普森的了解有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agreed. What do we know about this Thompson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是间谍活动吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, is this espionage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有外国政府牵涉在内吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is a foreign government involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点不确定  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's uncertain, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国安局正在倾尽全力追查他的下落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NSA's throwing all their resources into tracking him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠特克保证  一旦他获悉更多情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Whitaker promised to brief you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会立即向你汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as soon as he knows more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我们必须抢占先机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get ahead of this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nice to see you, Agent Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰  你是内务部的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, John, in your line of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常来说  见不到你反而是件好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's generally considered a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你和杰森·亚特伍德关系要好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I know that you were close with Jason Atwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这份友情也许会给你带来麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's a friendship that could cause problems for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也要调查我吗  -拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Am I under investigation, too? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很聪明  应该知道你必然牵扯其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're smart enough to know that you're wrapped up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳萨尔被谋杀时  你和杰森都在监狱里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were with Jason at the prison when Nassar was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审讯期间  你也和他一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were there with him during the interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次调查的意义何在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is the point of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该很清楚杰森不是谋杀犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You of all people know that Jason's not a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能忽视他的供词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't exactly ignore a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是预料之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this was so cut-and-dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你何必还要调查呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why are you doing an investigation at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  这理由我接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I'll bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果杰森·亚特伍德没杀马吉德·纳萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Jason Atwood didn't kill Majid Nassar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在的处境并没好到哪去  汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not doing yourself any favors, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道比起联邦检察官的查问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I know you'd rather answer my questions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更愿意回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than a federal prosecutor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们曾经立场一致  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We used to be on the same side. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你和杰森学会如何照章办事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we still would be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我多年前警告过你们的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you and Jason had ever learned how to play by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的立场仍然是一致的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like I warned you to years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是像现在这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, and, Hannah,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午  我会去看杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm paying Jason a visit this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的说词最好不要有出入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your stories better match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克  你能否把彼得·麦克利什的审核资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Chuck, think you can get the Peter MacLeish
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从资源管理情报系统中调出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}vetting files out of the RMD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-二十分钟后在我家见面  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and meet me at my house in 20 minutes? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是汉娜  到底发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, Hannah, what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了那我再向你解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll explain when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给艾米丽买了咖啡  从来没有我的份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You brought Emily coffee? You never bring me coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你找我干嘛  赛斯  -马吉德·纳萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you want, Seth? - Majid Nassar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没复活吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's still dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记不记得我和你说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember when I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媒体可能很想知道是谁杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the press was gonna want answers on who killed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-美国史上头号恐怖分子  -记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- the most-wanted terrorist in U.S. history? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实确实如此  非常迫切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm telling you they want answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得拖住他们  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you got to hold them off, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候才不用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是等《华盛顿邮报》开专栏呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the Post runs an op-ed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是等《泰晤士报》指责我们掩盖事实呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or when the Times accuses us of a cover-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统今天要和联调局的人会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, POTUS is meeting with the FBI today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争取点时间  让我们找出答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just buy us some time to get the answers we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你帮忙  下次我给你买咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you do, then coffee for you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百利·汤普森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gabriel Thompson just dumped
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚在维基解密上放出了大量政府文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a massive amount of government documents on WikiLeaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  维基解密吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seriously? WikiLeaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是揭发者的老把戏吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that, like, a whistleblower cliché?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些文件与前政府官员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not when the docs are all linked
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系起来的时候就不再是谣言了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to members of - the previous administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼也曾在前政府任职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which Kirkman served in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维基解密网上持续爆出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Material continues to be released via WikiLeaks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}国家安全局资料泄露\N国安局揭发者声称里士满政府内阁贪污腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里士满政府内阁成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}involving questionable activities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不法行为的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by members of President Richmond's cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据显示某些内阁成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It appears that several cabinet members
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾滥用职权收受贿赂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were abusing their power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大开方便之门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by receiving money in exchange for access.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他声称里士满政府内阁贪污腐败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so he's claiming that Richmond's cabinet was corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们可以排除他是间谍的嫌疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess we can take espionage off the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况有多糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎想象  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It looks a lot worse than it is, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  大概就是付费玩家模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, pay-for-play sort of things, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,财政部长拿了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Treasury Secretary was paid to give speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去银行家聚会上发表讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at corporate retreats for banking CEOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商务部长去海外研究的费用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commerce Secretary - took overseas research trips
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由外国游说团体承担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}paid for by foreign lobby groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The optics are terrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不属于重大犯罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's not exactly high crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们的行为的确是犯罪  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they are crimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从法律角度讲是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Counsel's office says yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但迄今为止  非议很少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but so far the blow-back's been minimal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他所提及的大部分人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and most of the people that he's referencing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经死于国会爆炸案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}died during the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩我的资料未被公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是问题之一  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's a problem, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  他说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的档案并未公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your files haven't been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他为何隐瞒我的档案  -这也许是个策略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why would he hold my files back? - Maybe it's a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要等到媒体极度兴奋之时再公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's waiting till the press is in a frenzy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就能吸引全国人民的关注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so he has the whole country's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我不想这么问您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I-I hate to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果势必会受到攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but if we're gonna get hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须要知道该如何去回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we need to know how to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  您有没有不可告人的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Mr. President, do you have anything to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有没有不可告人的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I have anything to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉这么问  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to ask, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想保护您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we just want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有什么好隐藏的  我没有秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I have nothing to hide. No secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会不会知道有关李奥亲生父亲的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it possible that he knows about Leo's paternity question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没什么好挖的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a non-story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像丽萨·乔丹一样  他们迟早会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'd find that out as quickly as Lisa Jordan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他知道我们正在审理亚特伍德认罪案件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he knows we're sitting on the Atwood confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经被一些媒体追问了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been getting hit from some national newspaper guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有审理任何案件  我们是在调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not sitting on anything. We're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦查出真凶  我们会立刻通知民众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As soon as we have answers, so will the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这个所谓的揭发者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So why would this so-called whistleblower
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有内阁成员的纳税申报单和银行记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}release every cabinet member's tax returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公之于众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their banking records,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独没有您的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}except yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我们可以花一天时间来推测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, - we can speculate all day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤普森先生可能会如何对付我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on what Mr. Thompson thinks he might have on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正需要做的是找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is we need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在国安局查清楚他到底偷走了什么之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until the NSA knows exactly what he's stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对国家安全都是个威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's a threat - to our national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  总统先生  我们会密切关注此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, sir, we'll stay on top of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-并随时向您报告  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- keep you posted. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直说好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说彼得·麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're saying that Peter MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是副总统候选人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the guy about to be confirmed as vice president,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉嫌策划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is somehow involved in the conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会爆炸案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that destroyed the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  这让人很难接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. It's a lot to process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母离婚曾给我造成很大的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My parents' divorce was a lot to process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这个还要更大  汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is next-level, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  但你把这些东西摆在我面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, but it's also hard to ignore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也无法视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you lay it all out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法索已经怀疑我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Foerstel's already suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能放过麦克利什  至少现在不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't back off MacLeish. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要能扳倒他的确凿证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need hard evidence against him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但目前我掌握的唯一证据是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the only evidence I have right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  晚上11点14分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I know. 11:14 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都查遍了  但一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked everywhere. I've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是为什么你要复查麦克利什的档案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, which is why you need to re-examine MacLeish's files
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看有没有相关之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and see if there's a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克  我知道你为了帮我冒着很大风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chuck, I know you're taking a risk by being here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要退出的话  我可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so if you needed to leave, I'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜  每次你来找我帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, when you come asking for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不会是易事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's never easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时甚至是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sometimes not even legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你既聪明又敬业  一般不会出错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're smart and dedicated and usually right,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以告诉我需要做什么就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so tell me what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷伯恩众议院办公楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  仅因你对总统有意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be honest, I'm not comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会去追查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}going after the "Miracle on the Potomac"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"联邦政府的生存奇迹"的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just because you've got a bone to pick with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员  你初来乍到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman, you're new here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来指点你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So let me give you a little bit of free advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿特区里全靠关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D.C. is all about relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this relationship, yours and mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞僵你我之间的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is not one you want to sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听证会只是确认  而非加冕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a confirmation, not a coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谨应总统所需并非我们的职责所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not our job to give the president what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为国家着想才是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our job is to determine what's best for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我失陪一会  里面见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you'll excuse me, I'll see you inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员  麦克利什夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman, Mrs. MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布尔  希望你今天别让他太轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimble, I hope you're not too easy on him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴能遇见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so glad I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能在开始前祝福你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have hated starting the day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会遗憾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without wishing you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much. I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you mind if I ask what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算如何对付我和柯克曼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have against Kirkman and myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't trust anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一辈子衣食无忧的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who has things handed to them in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是权利从天而降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上11点14分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}11:14 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美军退伍报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没看出任何东西  汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got nothing here, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来有点扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it sounds crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的线人说中了105室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but my source was right about Room 105.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was right about MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这条线索一定有用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so there's got to be something to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为能从这些档案的时间戳里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought that I would find those numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相似的时间点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on some of the time stamps on the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一这并不代表时间呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if it's not a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能是个日期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, what if it's a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个  这是他在阿富汗执行那次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at this. This... This is the after-action report
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为他赢得铜星勋章的任务的事后报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that earned him the Bronze Star in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2005年11月14号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}November 14, 2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}彼得·麦克利什\N美国陆军上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11月14号  PM\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}11/14 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P.M...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}P.M...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-彼得·麦克利什  -彼得·麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Peter MacLeish. - Peter MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这份文件还不是确凿的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but this document isn't exactly a smoking gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什的部队被塔利班所袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MacLeish's unit was attacked by the Taliban,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想救自己的战友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he managed to save most of his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份报告只是对他的勇敢与英雄主义的认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, this report's an endorsement of his bravery and heroism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  但第一次听到105室时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but Room 105, at a first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没想到这会是个防爆掩体  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}didn't look like a bomb shelter, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他的档案没写明事件的全过程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think his file isn't telling you the whole story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道当时在场的人是怎么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think that I'd like to hear from the men who were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他们是不是也这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether they saw things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为国会爆炸案的唯一幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be the only survivor of the Capitol bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}众议院司法委员会听证会\N关于麦克利什议员担任副总统事宜的听证会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不足以让我仕途亨通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, does not qualify me for higher office,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当柯克曼总统...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but when President Kirkman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什说得很精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MacLeish is crushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这家伙很适合上电视  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This guy was made for TV. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样还不能解决的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we don't wrap this up today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以直接讨伐霍斯拉滕蓄意拖延\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you can go hard after Hookstraten for holding it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候舆论肯定会向着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, public opinion will definitely be in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维基解密又有新内容了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another dump on WikiLeaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会议事录  电子邮件  立法汇报会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressional memos, e-mails, legislative briefings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没有柯克曼的把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't look like anything on Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  这些东西影响不到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, nothing here can touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看到有关黑兹尔顿参议员的泄漏记录了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen the leaked memo on Senator Hazelton?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要是能一直退休  国家会更美好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The country would've been better off if he'd stayed retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这是事实  但他的办公室刚打来电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that might be true, but his office just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们惹到了华盛顿特区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just pissed off the one man in Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最惹不起的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can't afford to piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么惹到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did we piss him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑兹尔顿参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Senator Hazelton?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次任期结束后他本已经退休\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He retired at the end of last term.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是国会爆炸案之后他复任了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He came back after the Capitol bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为佛特蒙州的州长指任了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the governor of Vermont appointed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他还刚被任命为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And just named the new chair
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议院拨款委员会新任主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Senate Appropriations Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位参议员权倾政界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The senator has tremendous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拨款委员会有权拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His committee can lock down
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们提议的任何债务  税收  和开支法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any debt, tax, spending bill we suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记录里什么内容这么严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what about the memo was so offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"黑泽尔顿参议员是个老淫魔"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Senator Hazelton is a lecherous old man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"只想猥亵女职员"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more accustomed to groping female staff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"而不想重用她们"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than promoting them."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这关我什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again, why is this my problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他要求你立刻解雇作者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he wants you to fire the author immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  作者是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, who's the author?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议员  请您理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Senator, please understand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所写的文字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that my words are in no way a reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与总统对您的看法毫无关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of how the president feels about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段话是很多年前写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was written years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我还不认识总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}long before I even met the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的所作所为让您难堪  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sincerely apologize for embarrassing you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这就够了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you think that's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议员  我知道你希望我解雇罗迪斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Senator, I know you want me to fire Ms. Rhodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经认识艾米丽很多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I've known Emily for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证  她是诚心道歉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can tell you her apology is sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是挺诚心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, she means it all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她现在害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now. When she's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当初污言秽语诽谤我的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She had a whole different attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,态度可不是现在这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when she first wrote that smear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时她就是个无名小卒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}back when she was a nobody,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府里的小啰喽  却狂妄自大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a jumped-up little House staffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我是财政委员会主席  为两任内阁效力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I was finance chairman, served in two cabinets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连续六次获选连任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}elected to six consecutive terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议员  我明白您的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again, Senator, I hear what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望能找到办法解决此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just trying to find us a way to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我放弃退休选择复任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I came out of retirement to serve again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为国家需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because my country needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚帮助你提名彼得·麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just helped your nominee, Peter MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速获得了参议院的认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through a speedy Senate confirmation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这样感谢我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this is my reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你手下的职员肆意中伤我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be libeled by one of your staffers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参议员  这些泄漏的文件对我们都很不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Senator, we were all thrown by these leaked documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该追查泄漏原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just think we should be going after
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查清幕后黑手  而不是讨伐文件作者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the people that leaked them, not the people that wrote them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的声名有损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you would feel differently
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概就不会这样想了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if it was your character that had been smeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我在参议院有多大权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know the power I wield in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你时间考虑  这件事该怎么解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll give you some time to consider in what way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该造成多大的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how publicly you want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是解决结果必须是她被辞退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she needs to be gone by the end of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-告退  -慢走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President. - Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管愿不愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好不要与他为敌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's not an enemy you want to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能推迟你未来三年的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can hold up your entire economic agenda
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个经济计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the next three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您必须让我辞职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to accept my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的提问  我能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate the question, and I -- and I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的公众生活一直毫无秘密可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, my public life's been an open book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小就谨记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever since I was a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·F·肯尼迪对于服役的号召\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I took to heart John F. Kennedy's call to service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望这次听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope over the course of this hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你们看到  我没有辜负这个使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're seeing how I lived up to that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为自己有资格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you think you're qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}众议院司法委员会\N确认麦克利什议员出任副总统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出任副总统一职吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the office of Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲从小就教我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father instilled in me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有比这更崇高的使命了  -你看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- that there is no higher calling... - Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副要当开国元勋的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like - he's channeling Camelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得也有点像肯尼迪家的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He even looks like a Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是11月14日任务中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the contact info
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什那八位队员的联系方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the eight members of MacLeish's unit on the 11/14 mission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们现居弗吉尼亚和马里兰州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}living in the Virginia-Maryland area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我一人之力没法搜查那么大范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't cover this much ground by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负责弗吉尼亚  我负责马里兰州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take Virginia. I'll take Maryland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当你非正式地晋升为外勤探员了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just consider this an unofficial battlefield promotion to field agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  用这台手机联系我  不要用你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also, call me on this, not your regular phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜欢躲在幕后操作电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm more of a behind-the-scenes computer guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克  我知道我的要求有点过分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chuck, I know I'm asking a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在我能信任的人少之又少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but there's a short list of people that I trust right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一个被冤枉入狱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of them is in jail for something he didn't do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一个就是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the other one is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把你的案子派给我时  我松了口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was relieved when they gave me your case
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道这世上能帮你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause I thought if anybody can help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非我莫属\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's gonna be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰  你永远都扮演不了好警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John, you could never play the good cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接问吧  别拐弯抹角了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just ask the questions, and let's get this thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么拒绝请辩护律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd you waive your right to an attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么要辩护的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have nothing to defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在到达监狱前就打算毒死纳萨尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you intended to poison Nassar before you arrived at the prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用盐包装着铊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had the Thallium
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在我的口袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in a salt packet hidden in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不担心会被监控录像拍到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you weren't at all concerned about surveillance footage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北厅的走廊里有个盲点区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a blind spot in the North Hall corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数年前一位探员告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An officer told me about it some years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防我需要私下会会某个犯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case I needed to have an off-the-record with a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等摄像头关掉后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I waited until we cleared the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过食品托盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I passed the food tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把盐放到了纳萨尔的盘子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put the salt in Nassar's plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道盘子是他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you know it was his?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是穆斯林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's Muslim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别为他准备了清真食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Specially prepared halal meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能核实他所说的这一切吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we verify everything he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的团队正在查  先生  但至今为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My team's working on it, sir, but so far, everything he said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的供词符合现场取得的法医证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}matches the forensic evidence taken from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟杰森·阿特伍德是同期吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came up with Jason Atwood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在匡提科时同班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were in the same class at Quantico.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次任务是一起做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had our first assignments together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you ever imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是犯下这种罪行的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he was capable of committing such a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在职业责任办公室十三年了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've worked in the Office of Professional Responsibility for 13 years, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我们也不愿把人往坏处想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We may not want to think the worst of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时我们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but sometimes they leave us no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到了国安局揭发者的最新消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have an update on the NSA whistleblower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总统先生  -先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. President. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到他了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们找到加百利·汤普森了  -他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We found Gabriel Thompson. - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他潜逃了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's on foreign soil, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我们冻结了他的护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we froze his passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他是怎么逃出去的  -他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How did he get out? - He didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在我们旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's right down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在委内瑞拉大使馆内寻求庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's seeking asylum in the Venezuelan Embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国与之没有引渡条约  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No extradition treaty with the U.S., sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我说他现在就在华盛顿特区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're telling me he's right here in Washington, D.C.,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们却无计可施\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we can't touch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们不能把加百利·汤普森转交给贵国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I cannot turn over Gabril Thompson,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在寻求庇护  我们必须尊重他的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's seeking asylum, and we must respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使先生  拒不交出一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Ambassador, there is a big difference
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贩卖毒品的轻罪犯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between not sending back a petty criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一个对国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was arrested for marijuana
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成威胁的逃犯之间是有很大区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a fugitive who we consider a threat to our national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格地说不是这样  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not technically, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法决定贵国法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't dictate your nation's laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反之亦然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you cannot dictate mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委内瑞拉方面还不会把他交出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Venezuela won't give him back...yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来重新制定策略  看有什么结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll circle back to the drawing board, see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑兹尔顿的事情刻不容缓  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still on the clock with Hazelton, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件一件来吧  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One thing at a time, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件一件来  什么时候的习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One thing at a time? Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你第一次去阿富汗执行任务的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now, during your first tour in Afghanistan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因为英勇作战为被授予青铜星章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were awarded a Bronze Star for combat bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}乔治先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你尽可能回忆在2005年11月14日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now, can you please describe the events of November 14, 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the best of your recollection?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能尽力地回忆一下2005年11月14日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you describe the events of November 14, 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the best of your recollection?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什队长带领着一队游骑兵特种部队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain MacLeish led a Ranger Special Forces unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了距马尔扎很远的一个阿富汗村庄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...into a remote Afghani village outside of Marja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚进村就受到了路边炸弹的袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As soon as we moved in, our unit hit an IED, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遭到了塔利班武装力量的伏击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we were ambushed by Taliban forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛乱分子武装精良\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Insurgents were heavily armed, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们瞬间被敌人压制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we were pinned down almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤亡惨重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hit, bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半人在顽强求生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half my men clinging to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一半则瑟瑟发抖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other half frozen in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我属于后半部分的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I -- And I include myself in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本能使然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I acted on pure instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什队长独自一人与叛军战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain MacLeish returned enemy fire single-handedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击退了叛乱分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}drove back the insurgents...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们及时获得了救治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...allowing medics to get to us in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天由我负责的任务失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I presided over a failed mission that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有攻下村庄  并且损失惨重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't take the village, and we lost a lot of good men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能活下来多亏了麦克利什队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alive - because of Captain MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个词可以描绘他那样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So there's only one word to use to describe a man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的奖章表彰了我的英勇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's what my medal says I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是说到英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很惭愧  我只是做了常人会做的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I only did what anyone in my position would have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't make me a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个今天各位看到的普通人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It simply makes me who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个他队伍里的人回答都完全一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every guy in his platoon says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜猜  他是一个英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me guess -- that he's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我也得到了同样的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. Same answer I got, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你的线人搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe your informant was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者也许所有人事先统一了口径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe everyone got the same talking points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有一个采访要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got one interview left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到最后我不会放弃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not giving up till it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你在我的办公室呆的时间比我还长吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know you spend a lot more time in my office than I do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要讨论一下黑兹尔顿的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to talk about Hazelton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌张  这件事会平息的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it. It'll blow over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给我一点时间  -不  不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just give it some time. - No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统不能把我放在第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the president can't put me first,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为让这个国家复苏的关键立法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not before critical legislation we need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我更为重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to get this country back on its feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经济刺激法案 创造工作岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stimulus bills, job creation --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都需要拨款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those things go through appropriations,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要通过黑泽尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through Hazelton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  总统在我泄露艾尔萨卡视频后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, the President didn't accept my resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有接受我的辞呈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I leaked the Al-Sakar video.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时都不怎么了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He barely even knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他最信任的顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're his most trusted adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他不会接受的  我知道  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's not gonna accept yours. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你必须接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why you're gonna accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护总统是你的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's your job to protect the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是要保护他不要被自己伤害 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even when that means protecting him from himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  你有没有想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, have you ever considered the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不愿意接受你的辞呈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he won't accept your resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为他需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he needs you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不只是他需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以等会再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no. - You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -留下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is it? - Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就提醒过你这种情况了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what I like to call "I told you so" --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一份全国的媒体名录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a list of every media outlet in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他们请求对总统进行独家专访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and their requests for an exclusive with the president
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to discuss, among other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳萨尔谋杀案调查事宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Nassar murder investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接拒绝他们吧  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feel free to tell them no, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不能怪他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't blame them for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁不想跟总统聊一聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, who doesn't want five minutes with the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你刚说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说谁不想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said who doesn't want --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟总统聊一聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}five minutes with the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  打给委内瑞拉大使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, call the Venezuelan Ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我我这就过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you tell him I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-刚刚发生了什么  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What just happened? - No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太抱歉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有意识到你丈夫已经去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I didn't realize your husband had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他瞒着我再服兵役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He re-upped without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说不能坐视不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he couldn't leave things the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟突击队的首次出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And his first tour with the Ranger unit --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由彼得·麦克利什议员指挥的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that was commanded by Congressman Peter MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂文不爱说他服役时的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steven never liked talking about his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至没有意识到他很喜欢他的部队生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't even realize he enjoyed his time in the Army
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到部队把他的储物柜寄回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until one day the Army shipped home his foot locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面全都是纪念品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In it were all these mementos --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他赢得的奖章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, medals that he had won,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的老战友的信件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}letters from his old buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一大把服役时的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had tons of pictures of his tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 介意我看看那个储物柜吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sarah, do you mind if I take a look at that foot locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤普森先生  我是亚伦·肖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Thompson, I'm Aaron Shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chief of Staff to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在在委内瑞拉国土  肖尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on Venezuelan soil, Mr. Shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能逮捕我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚外交法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm well aware of diplomatic law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CNN说我想要激进的政府透明公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CNN says I want radical transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《纽约时报》说我想要无政府状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The New York Times says I want anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有何猜想呢  肖尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your guess, Mr. Shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟总统聊一聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five minutes with the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么这么确定我想见总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What makes you so sure I want to see the President?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在网上发布的内容非常详细\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been very specific with what you've posted on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先你攻击了里士满前总统的所有内阁成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First you attacked members of the Richmond cabinet --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独没有攻击柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}every one of them, except Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着你又转向他最信任的顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you went after his most trusted adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确保了他注意到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You made sure he'd notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是八九不离十了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I getting warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.24,0:24:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.34,0:24:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这方法找自由世界的领袖会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell of a way to get an audience with
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是费尽周折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the leader of the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都只能尽全力  肖尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We use the tools we have, Mr. Shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  但是你伤害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but you've hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是永久性地伤害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}perhaps irreparably, a good friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.01,0:24:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统的一位至交好友也是他忠诚的顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a brilliant, loyal adviser to the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.61,0:24:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你还需要得到我的许可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and being that I'm the one person
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能见到总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who can grant you access to the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要允许你见总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why should I reward you with his time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.77,0:24:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不把艾米丽·罗迪斯推到风口上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I had to hang Emily Rhodes in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.45,0:24:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吸引你的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to get your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我同样也能拯救她的职业生涯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm also the guy that can save her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.82,0:26:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都参加了那次任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were on the same mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.48,0:26:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特兰和麦克利什认识彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catalan and MacLeish know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.36,0:26:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11/14  这才是线人想让我知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}11/14 -- That's what my source wanted me to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.63,0:26:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.86,0:26:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这算不上确凿证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I know it's not a smoking gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.27,0:26:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这已经比我们一小时前更接近真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it puts us a hell of a lot closer than it did an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克  我需要进入反恐怖行动联合数据库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chuck, I'm going to need into the counter-terror joint database.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.12,0:26:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}该用户已被锁定  无法登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.61,0:26:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -你还在听吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.56,0:26:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}该用户已被锁定  无法登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.72,0:26:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在吗  -他们屏蔽了我的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello? - They shut me out of my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.67,0:26:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -我的账号登陆不上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - My login's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.84,0:26:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法索肯定知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Foerstel must know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.51,0:26:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你未经许可就把麦克利什的档案带出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you took MacLeish's files off-site without clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.05,0:26:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在朝我走来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is heading right towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.23,0:26:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说他也在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means he's gonna be looking for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.57,0:26:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜  不要回来  想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah, don't come back. Find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.95,0:26:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.46,0:26:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百利·汤普森说想和我见面吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gabriel Thompson wants to set a meeting with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.30,0:26:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.95,0:26:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一号楼里他把这个给了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to facilitate one, he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.80,0:26:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是什么  -是他表示诚意的东西  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is it? - It's a show of good faith, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.64,0:27:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面的东西能够证明艾米丽说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's proof that everything Emily said
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.85,0:27:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有关于黑兹尔顿参议员的事情都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about Senator Hazelton is true --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.71,0:27:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面记录了参议员一年内与一位助手的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A year's worth of inappropriate e-mails, text messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.76,0:27:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不雅邮件  短信和聊天记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}chats with a Senate page.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.68,0:27:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经同意停止泄露文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's agreed to stop releasing files
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.42,0:27:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且交出他所有的东西了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and hand over everything he has?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.72,0:27:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意见他的话  是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you meet with him, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定邀请一个窃取保密文件的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure inviting a man who stole classified documents
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.60,0:27:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来白宫是个好的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into the White House is an option,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.66,0:27:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论他手里有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter what he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们确实需要解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we do have to take care of this business
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑兹尔顿参议员这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with Senator Hazelton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.76,0:27:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看是不是现在就可以把他带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see if we can get him over here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.56,0:27:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好的  先生  -谢谢  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Thank you, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.31,0:27:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍斯拉滕议员  上次我们约定过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman Hookstraten, last time we spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.97,0:27:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会向你持续汇报国会大厦爆炸案的进展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I'd keep you updated on the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.54,0:27:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在105房间找到你想要的东西了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you find what you were looking for in room 105?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.08,0:27:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙拖延麦克利什的听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I need you to delay the MacLeish hearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.89,0:27:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议员  我不能在电话里详说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman, I can't talk about this over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.81,0:27:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我找到了能够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm working a lead
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.61,0:27:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把彼得·麦克利什拉下台的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could prove damning to Peter MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.84,0:27:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还需要一些时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I need time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:28:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士小姐  你这是要让我用名声做担保\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Wells, you're asking me to put my reputation on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.31,0:28:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.54,0:28:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能给我的全部时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As much as you can give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.08,0:28:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.19,0:28:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你抽出时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for taking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我说得已经很明确了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I made myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.13,0:28:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么还在这里工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is she still working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because, Senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.44,0:28:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能决定谁在这里工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the one who chooses which of my staffers I let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我想证明一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I try to make a point
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.49,0:28:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会用到不光彩的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by not starting out with my best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.48,0:28:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗迪斯女士说的所有关于你的事情都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything Ms. Rhodes said about you is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.11,0:28:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我有证据可以证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I have the proof to back it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.85,0:28:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.31,0:28:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该听闻了我们最近和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you've heard of our recent interactions
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.47,0:28:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百利·汤普森的交涉  那个国安局告密者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with Gabriel Thompson, the NSA whistleblower?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.15,0:28:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止  他的爆料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So far, everything that he's released
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.83,0:28:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都百分百准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has proved to be 100% accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  他有你的确凿信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, he has you dead to rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.47,0:28:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个十八岁的参议员助手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An 18-year-old Senate page.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.69,0:29:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是勒索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is extortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.09,0:29:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.88,0:29:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是给你看事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am simply presenting you with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.60,0:29:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勒索是以美国经济稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Extortion would be threatening
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.07,0:29:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为要挟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to compromise the American economic stability
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.63,0:29:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胁迫我开除幕僚的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless I fire one of my staff members
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.18,0:29:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她写了你不喜欢的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because she wrote something that you didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.55,0:29:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结婚三十五年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a wife of 35 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是两个好孩子的父亲  三个孩子的祖父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two beautiful children, three grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.76,0:29:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早些时候  你为了陪他们退休了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Earlier, you retired to spend time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.27,0:29:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我强烈建议你考虑再次退休\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I strongly suggest you consider doing that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.77,0:29:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想再待一会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think you want to stick around a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.29,0:29:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是  我没有别的地方想去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luckily, there's no place I'd rather be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.49,0:30:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.88,0:30:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}餐馆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.59,0:30:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, it turns out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.94,0:30:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国最喜爱的副总统人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that America's favorite vice presidential candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.14,0:30:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和中情局头号通缉的雇佣兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the CIA's most wanted mercenary
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.31,0:30:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.70,0:30:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你应该不会相信这是巧合吧  -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I guess you're not buying it's a coincidence? - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.52,0:30:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果卡特兰的确为11/14任务收集情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Catalan worked intel on the 11/14 mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.10,0:30:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中情局应该会留有档案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the CIA would have a file on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去调档案了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you pull it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.32,0:30:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有的话我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have if there was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.05,0:30:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在逗我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有人销毁了  -所以我更深入地调查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Someone buried it? - So I looked deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.06,0:30:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.08,0:30:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由战地中情局联络员写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was written by an Agency liaison on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.69,0:30:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟麦克利什说的不太一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not quite the same story that MacLeish has been telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.10,0:30:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"2005年11月14日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"On November 14, 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.56,0:31:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其队员被塔利班狙击手射杀后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a Ranger unit massacred a series of Afghani villages
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.24,0:31:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一支突击小队血洗了数个阿富汗村庄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after several of their unit had been killed by a Taliban sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24小时内屠杀3座村庄  死伤无数”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}3 villages in 24 hours. Countless dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.47,0:31:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼洗白了这件事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Pentagon whitewashed this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.80,0:31:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得·麦克利什不是什么战争英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter MacLeish isn't a war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.87,0:31:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他是战争犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he's a war criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.04,0:31:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了艾米丽的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard about Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.12,0:31:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是解决了那个危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's one crisis resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在看另一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I'm reading about the other one --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.84,0:31:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百利·汤普森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gabriel Thompson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.65,0:31:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他的心理档案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is his psychological profile
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由国务院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}courtesy of the State Department,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.26,0:31:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦执法部门和国安局提供的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}federal law enforcement, and the NSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.28,0:31:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯  我到底漏了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, what the hell am I missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.33,0:31:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像每次我转过头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it seems like every time I turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.21,0:31:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就发现有人忠心耿耿地服务国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's someone who's served this country faithfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.91,0:31:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后突然就打算背弃国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then out of the blue, decides to turn against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在说告密者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you talking about the whistleblower
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.95,0:31:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是杰森·亚特伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or Jason Atwood now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:31:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.48,0:32:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国安局分析员变成了叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}NSA analyst turns traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.09,0:32:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局副局长杀了人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deputy FBI director commits murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.68,0:32:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.43,0:32:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭直觉怎么看汤普森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does your gut say about Thompson?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.05,0:32:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撇开我的国家安全团队的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, despite the advice of my National Security Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统办公厅的批文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the protocols of the Office of the Presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.62,0:32:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我自己的常识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and my own common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这家伙没有疯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I don't think this guy's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.10,0:32:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.69,0:32:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道一旦他离开了大使馆的保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he knows once he leaves the protection of the embassy,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.12,0:32:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他免不了长久的牢狱之灾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's going to prison for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.75,0:32:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他想和你面谈的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So whatever the reason for wanting to sit down with you is,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定重要到让他不惜舍弃性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it must be pretty important for him to trade in his life for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我想不通的部分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the part I can't figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.19,0:32:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会想通的  只要调查得再深入一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will. Just need to look deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.11,0:33:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清空你的口袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empty your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.11,0:33:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a few moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.00,0:33:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会押送你去联邦监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're going to be taking you to federal prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.68,0:33:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我长话短说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I need to make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.38,0:33:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有一个继女叫夏洛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you had a stepdaughter named Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.45,0:33:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是埃尔斯沃思议员办公室的实习生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who was an intern in Congressman Ellsworth's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.07,0:33:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她参加了国情咨文演讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that she was at the State of the Union
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.71,0:33:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果在爆炸中丧生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and died in the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.70,0:33:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的生父  不同的姓氏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Different birth father, different last name
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.07,0:33:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人难以把这一系列事串起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}made it harder to make the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.46,0:34:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你把她从襁褓里抚养成人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also understand that you raised her since she was a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.92,0:34:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她也是你的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so she was yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.77,0:34:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不该有白发人送黑发人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Children should never die before their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.02,0:34:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  不应该\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, they should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.48,0:34:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的遭遇深表遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I am very sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.29,0:34:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.60,0:34:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as a father,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.64,0:34:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你的愤怒和悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand your anger and your grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.54,0:34:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这仍然不能回答我的关键问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it still doesn't answer my main question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你牺牲了这么多就为了与我见上这一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sacrificed a great deal to have this meeting with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.83,0:34:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.50,0:34:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一个我能信任的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I needed someone I could trust
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.71,0:34:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以确保这样的攻击不会再发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make sure an attack like that never happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么让你认为你可以信任我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what makes you think you can trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I did my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.87,0:34:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读了你发的每一封邮件  写的每一份文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}read every e-mail you sent, every document you wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的道德观无可挑剔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your ethics are above reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.61,0:34:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用说每四条短信就有一条是发给孩子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention every fourth text you send is to your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.74,0:35:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个证物袋里是我的零钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inside that evidence bag is my pocket change.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.76,0:35:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有一个假的25美分硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a fake coin, a quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.90,0:35:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那其中是我偷走的硬盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inside it is the hard drive I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.97,0:35:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有做任何备份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not make copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么把这个给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you giving this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.87,0:35:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你有比我更大的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you have much bigger problems than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.30,0:35:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交接车辆已经备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Transport is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.48,0:35:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随意把文件12-80C给别人看  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Careful who you show file 12-80C to, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.87,0:35:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  那个人放弃了他的事业和自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, that man gave up his career and his freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了那个硬盘上的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for what's on this hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.46,0:35:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要知道背后的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.11,0:36:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个笔记本是物理隔离的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This laptop's air-gapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.26,0:36:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果这个硬盘上有恶意软件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if there's malware on this drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.63,0:36:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这一台计算机会被感染\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it'll only affect this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.56,0:36:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解码软件已经在运行中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}De-encryption software's already running.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道这些的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.07,0:36:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我被分配给你做保镖前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I was assigned to your protective detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.71,0:36:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我辗转于各种调查工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I rotated through investigations,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.48,0:36:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁评估  还有我们的技术部门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}threat assessment, and our technical department.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.07,0:36:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在计算机编程方面干了两年半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}2 1/2 years staring at computer code.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.17,0:36:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想说  我更喜欢给你工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just say I like working for you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.60,0:36:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.69,0:36:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  在我们清楚这上面到底有什么之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, until we know exactly what this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.36,0:36:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要告诉别人这件事  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want it to stay between us. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.26,0:36:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.28,0:36:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.43,0:36:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍斯拉滕议员刚刚打来电话要求延期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman Hookstraten just called for an extended recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.82,0:36:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要推迟麦克利什的听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's delaying MacLeish's hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.64,0:36:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.47,0:36:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很狡猾不肯说  但是有个众议院的人说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's being cagey, but a House staffer says
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.03,0:36:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有关于麦克利什的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's got information on MacLeish
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.21,0:36:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会对听证会影响很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could be critical to the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.59,0:36:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正努力获取更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're trying to find out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.87,0:36:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女议员和我常常意见相左\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Congresswoman and I don't agree on much,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.53,0:36:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她不是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but she's not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.26,0:36:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定认为她手里他的重要信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must think that she's got something substantial on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.19,0:36:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则她不会冒这个风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}otherwise she wouldn't risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.49,0:37:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把麦克利什叫来  -是的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get me MacLeish. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.45,0:37:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  我会确保你不被打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mike, I'll make sure you're not disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.60,0:37:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不妨开门见山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I guess I'll just get right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.06,0:37:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍斯拉滕议员认为她有你的把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman Hookstraten thinks she has information on you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.57,0:37:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够左右听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that can alter the hearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.89,0:37:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.68,0:37:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.97,0:37:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你有事情想要告诉我  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if there's something you need to tell me, Peter,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请现在就说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前告诉你的一切都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, everything I've ever told you has been true,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.22,0:37:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对我的祖国忠心耿耿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I served my country loyally,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.18,0:37:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身心投入到我的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I dedicated myself to my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.43,0:37:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我选区的人民  和整个国家中去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the people of my district, the entire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.95,0:37:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.93,0:37:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解我必须得问问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}okay, I hope you understand I had to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.25,0:37:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很感谢你的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and thank you for your support,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.16,0:37:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道  这对我来说真的很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know it always -- it always means the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.98,0:37:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉麻烦你了  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to trouble you, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.33,0:37:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.65,0:37:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告辞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you know, sir, there --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.58,0:37:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事一直困扰着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's something that's been nagging at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.40,0:37:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森·阿特伍德供认谋杀了马吉德·纳萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason Atwood confessed to murdering Majid Nassar,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.91,0:37:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最器重的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the agent he valued the most --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.88,0:38:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜·威尔士特别探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Agent Hannah Wells --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.76,0:38:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.55,0:38:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说她在爆炸中失去了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I heard she lost someone in the bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这之间有什么联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe that's got something to do with it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.82,0:38:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的注意力总是在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She seemed to be a bit obsessed with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.03,0:38:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望她不会试着用阴谋论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hope she isn't trying to convince the speaker
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.00,0:38:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来说服议长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of any, uh, fantasy or conspiracy theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.26,0:38:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for letting me know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.60,0:38:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会注意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.39,0:38:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.86,0:38:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good night, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}众议院
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.91,0:38:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时候刚好  威尔士探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells, just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.06,0:38:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了关于彼得·麦克利什的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found the evidence I was looking for on Peter MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.53,0:38:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在去议会的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll explain everything when I get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.89,0:38:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到了后会解释一切的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just heading up Constitution now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.61,0:38:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.73,0:38:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congressman George,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.38,0:38:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让委员会集合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gather the rest of the committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.02,0:38:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的证人还有10分钟就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my witness will be here in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.88,0:38:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.04,0:39:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前没有机会谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't get a chance to thank you earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.91,0:39:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保住了我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for saving my job today,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.37,0:39:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举手之劳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't even mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.35,0:39:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个好员工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're a good employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.17,0:39:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做这么多只为了留住个好员工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did all of that to keep a good employee around.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.63,0:39:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  或许我有其他的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I may have other reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.42,0:39:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有工作要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I have work to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.15,0:39:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想起了那些理由  记得告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you think of any of those reasons, let me know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.92,0:39:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Emily,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.68,0:39:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚完成工作后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you're finished with work tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.25,0:39:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃个晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.80,0:39:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.71,0:40:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.89,0:40:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了12-80C文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I located File 12-80C,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.76,0:40:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你一起打开看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was waiting for you before I opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.01,0:40:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.41,0:41:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁创建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who created this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.34,0:41:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.27,0:41:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国政府创建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}United States Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.05,0:41:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2013年11月17号创建\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}November 17, 2013.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.13,0:41:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}威胁评估特别委员会  五角大楼 顶级加密
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.29,0:41:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁评估特别委员会  五角大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Committee for Threat Assessment, Pentagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.02,0:41:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶级加密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Classified Top Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.52,0:41:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是国会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the Capitol bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.51,0:41:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一样的模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right down to the same ordinance,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.54,0:41:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在评估安全漏洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're assessing our security vulnerabilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在爆炸发生数年前就演习过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they war-gamed this out years before it even happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.25,0:41:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府中有人把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone inside the U.S. Government
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝图交给了马吉德·纳萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}handed over the blueprints to Majid Nassar
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.11,0:41:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致了国会被炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.58,0:41:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们中间出了个叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a traitor among us.

